---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contact & Booking | Coastal Soil Solutions
description: Book a soil consultation or ask about FPJ stockist accounts. Email tomlinsonbc@gmail.com or call 778-991-6202. Serving the Lower Mainland.
permalink: /contact/
---
<section class="hero hero--page" aria-label="Contact">
  <div class="hero__media">
    <img src="{{ '/assets/img/contact-hero-garden-tools-1280.webp' | url }}"
         srcset="{{ '/assets/img/contact-hero-garden-tools-640.webp' | url }} 640w, {{ '/assets/img/contact-hero-garden-tools-1280.webp' | url }} 1280w, {{ '/assets/img/contact-hero-garden-tools-1920.webp' | url }} 1920w"
         sizes="100vw" width="1920" height="1080" fetchpriority="high"
         alt="Garden tools leaning against a cedar raised bed in evening light.">
  </div>
  <div class="container hero__content">
    <h1>Talk to Coastal Soil Solutions</h1>
    <p class="lead">Consultations, soil tests, FPJ stockist accounts and school programs — one conversation starts all of them.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" aria-labelledby="book-heading" id="book">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="book-heading">Book directly</h2>
    <div class="notice" style="margin-top: var(--space-4)">
      <p><strong>Online booking is coming soon.</strong> Until it is live, email or call and we will find a time within a couple of days.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top: var(--space-6)">
      <a class="btn btn--primary" href="mailto:{{ site.email }}?subject=Booking%20request">Email {{ site.email }}</a>
      <a class="btn btn--secondary" href="tel:{{ site.phone_tel }}">Call {{ site.phone }}</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--tight" aria-labelledby="details-heading">
  <div class="container prose">
    <h2 id="details-heading">Details</h2>
    <p><strong>Email.</strong> <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a></p>
    <p><strong>Phone.</strong> <a href="tel:{{ site.phone_tel }}">{{ site.phone }}</a></p>
    <p><strong>Service area.</strong> {{ site.area }} — {{ site.area_cities }} and surrounding communities.</p>
    <p><strong>Instagram.</strong> <a href="{{ site.instagram }}" rel="me noopener">@coastalsoilsolutions</a></p>
    <p>When you write, a sentence on what you grow and where helps us come prepared.</p>
  </div>
</section>
